  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libsamplerate</title>

    <para><application>libsamplerate</application> is a sample rate converter 
    for audio.</para>

    &lfs71_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
